    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="transcript" id="P90-59">
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Like trains of cars on tracks of plush</l>
                    <l>I hear the level bee:</l>
                    <l>A jar across the flowers goes,</l>
                    <l>Their velvet masonry</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Withstands until the sweet assault</l>
                    <l>Their chivalry consumes,</l>
                    <l>While he, victorious, tilts away</l>
                    <l>To vanquish other blooms.</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>His feet are shod with gauze,</l>
                    <l>His helmet is of gold;</l>
                    <l>His breast, a single onyx</l>
                    <l>With chrysoprase, inlaid.</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>His labor is a chant,</l>
                    <l>His idleness a tune;</l>
                    <l>Oh, for a bee's experience</l>
                    <l>Of clovers and of noon!</l>
                </lg>

            </div>     
        </body>
